<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_fa53642f-2212-479f-85dd-18e4ae07c2da" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="WA"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H9P1</sptc><title id="_1df682e0-8409-4325-a94c-578414a15ab1">Water use efficiency</title><archive-num>2019: WA 2.2(a)</archive-num><subclause id="_4cc04949-987e-4521-855b-2aa599c70825" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_3ee38ae0-4746-4a94-b4a6-37bf724d71d8">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building must have features that, to the degree necessary, facilitate the efficient use of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1250_0.7.0.xml#_762d6a54-e28c-400b-b9c5-5fceac019a05" id="_abd67bc8-5f38-4d51-a7ff-076280fda208" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drinking water</xref> appropriate to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_483b12ad-2d9e-4f98-b01c-d6ee60673740">the geographic location of the building; and</li><li id="_0942335c-bd89-46b8-87d0-61a9f470f965">the available <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1250_0.7.0.xml#_762d6a54-e28c-400b-b9c5-5fceac019a05" id="_33caf477-5761-437e-9789-e7d0cea20746" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drinking water</xref> supply of the building; and</li><li id="_c4968319-07b4-442f-a45a-f0c1e66f3497">the function and use of the building.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_cdd4411d-78a2-4bb3-8327-0782b01f11b6"><callout-type ncc-info-type="application"/><p>WA H9P1 only applies to Class 1 buildings, associated Class 10a buildings and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_ae948d17-a232-4149-8732-03ddde9c29fc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pools</xref> associated with a Class 1 building.</p></callout></clause>